---
import BaseLayout from "../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Monthly Deep Dive | 1H Crypto" description="Monthly Bitcoin & Ethereum deep analysis combining Al Brooks price action with on-chain data. Medium-term trade planning." lang="en" activeNav="monthly">
<script type="application/ld+json">{JSON.stringify({
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Article",
  "headline": "Monthly Deep Dive",
  "description": "Monthly Bitcoin & Ethereum deep analysis combining Al Brooks price action with on-chain data.",
  "inLanguage": "en-US",
  "datePublished": "2026-01-31T20:00:00+08:00",
  "dateModified": new Date().toISOString(),
  "author": { "@type": "Person", "name": "1H Crypto Trader" },
  "publisher": {
    "@type": "Organization",
    "name": "1H Crypto",
    "logo": { "@type": "ImageObject", "url": "https://1hcrypto.com/favicon.svg" }
  },
  "mainEntityOfPage": { "@type": "@id", "@id": "https://1hcrypto.com/en/monthly/" }
})}</script>

<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12">
  <div class="mb-10">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Monthly Deep Dive</h1>
    <p class="text-[var(--text-muted)] text-sm">Published last day of each month · Medium-term structure analysis + on-chain insights + next month trade plan.</p>
    <div class="mt-4 flex items-center gap-3 text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]">
      <span class="px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-[var(--border)]">Last day 20:00 Beijing Time</span>
      <span>|</span>
      <span>Covers BTC & ETH monthly structure</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Latest Monthly -->
  <div class="mb-12">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-6">
      <div class="w-1 h-5 rounded-full bg-primary"></div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Latest Deep Dive</h2>
      <span class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)] ml-2">2026-05</span>
    </div>

    <div class="card p-6 sm:p-8">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-6">
        <span class="text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-blue-500/10 text-blue-400 border border-blue-500/20">BTC/USDT</span>
        <span class="text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-purple-500/10 text-purple-400 border border-purple-500/20">ETH/USDT</span>
        <span class="text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-amber-500/10 text-amber-400 border border-amber-500/20">Monthly</span>
      </div>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">BTC Monthly Deep Dive: Breakout Imminent, Preparing for New Highs</h3>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-3 mb-6">
        <div class="card p-3 text-center">
          <div class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)] mb-1">Month Open</div>
          <div class="text-sm font-bold text-white">$68,500</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card p-3 text-center">
          <div class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)] mb-1">Month Close</div>
          <div class="text-sm font-bold text-green-400">$73,850</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card p-3 text-center">
          <div class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)] mb-1">Monthly Gain</div>
          <div class="text-sm font-bold text-green-400">+7.8%</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card p-3 text-center">
          <div class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)] mb-1">Paper P&L</div>
          <div class="text-sm font-bold text-green-400">+$12,400</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4 mb-6 text-sm text-[var(--text-muted)] leading-relaxed">
        <p><strong class="text-white">Monthly Structure:</strong> May closed as a large bullish bar, closing above EMA20 ($70,200). Two consecutive bullish monthly bars. May low ($68,300) > April low ($65,800), confirming Higher Low structure. Monthly timeframe is in an uptrend after healthy retest.</p>
        <p><strong class="text-white">Al Brooks Monthly Signal:</strong> May's K-line is a Strong Bull Bar (close near high, body > 80%), consistent with Al Brooks' "Trend Continuation" pattern. April's Doji Bar failed to extend the downtrend; bulls defended $65,000 demand zone, confirming a mid-term bottom.</p>
        <p><strong class="text-white">On-chain Data:</strong> May saw exchange net outflow of -48,200 BTC (source: CryptoQuant), the largest single-month outflow since 2026. LTH (Long-Term Holder) addresses increased +32,100 BTC. Chips moved from exchanges to cold wallets—sell pressure reduction signal is clear.</p>
        <p><strong class="text-white">ETH/BTC Ratio:</strong> ETH/BTC rose from 0.045 to 0.052 in May. ETH monthly performance exceeded BTC for the first time since Dec 2025. Alt season expectation is warming, but wait for BTC dominance to break below 50% for confirmation.</p>
        <p><strong class="text-white">Next Month Key Levels:</strong> Resistance $78,000 (monthly prior high) · $82,000 (psychological). Support $70,000 (EMA20) / $65,800 (monthly HL). If $70,000 breaks, structure turns neutral—re-evaluate.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="border-t border-[var(--border)] pt-4 mb-4">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-2">Next Month Trade Plan (June)</p>
        <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-400 mt-0.5">▶</span>If retest $71,000–$72,000 and 1H shows Bullish Engulfing Bar, go long. TP $76,000, SL $69,500</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-400 mt-0.5">▶</span>If breakout above $75,000 with volume expansion, chase. TP $78,000, SL $73,000</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-red-400 mt-0.5">▶</span>If breakdown below $69,500 and 1H shows Bearish Engulfing Bar, short (scalp). TP $67,000, SL $71,000</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-[var(--text-muted)] mt-0.5">▶</span>Risk management: max 2% per trade, total exposure ≤ 10%</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="border-t border-[var(--border)] pt-4 mb-4">
        <p class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)] mb-2">This Month's Related Trades</p>
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <a href="/en/trading/" class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 rounded-lg bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/[0.08] transition-colors no-underline">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-green-500/10 text-green-400">Long</span>
              <span class="text-sm text-white">BTC/USDT</span>
            </div>
            <div class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]">5/03 Entry · 5/28 TP →</div>
          </a>
          <a href="/en/trading/" class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 rounded-lg bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/[0.08] transition-colors no-underline">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-green-500/10 text-green-400">Long</span>
              <span class="text-sm text-white">ETH/USDT</span>
            </div>
            <div class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]">5/10 Entry · Holding →</div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <a href="/en/daily/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm text-primary hover:underline">View This Month's Daily Analysis →</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Historical Monthly -->
  <div class="mb-8">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-6">
      <div class="w-1 h-5 rounded-full bg-[var(--border)]"></div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Historical Deep Dives</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="space-y-3">
      <a href="#" class="card p-4 flex items-center justify-between hover:border-primary/30 transition-colors no-underline">
        <div>
          <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-1">2026-04 Monthly Deep Dive</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]">BTC monthly Doji · Consolidation · Paper +$3,200</div>
        </div>
        <span class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]">→</span>
      </a>
      <a href="#" class="card p-4 flex items-center justify-between hover:border-primary/30 transition-colors no-underline">
        <div>
          <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-1">2026-03 Monthly Deep Dive</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]">BTC broke $70,000 · Large monthly bull bar · Paper +$15,800</div>
        </div>
        <span class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]">→</span>
      </a>
      <a href="#" class="card p-4 flex items-center justify-between hover:border-primary/30 transition-colors no-underline">
        <div>
          <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-1">2026-02 Monthly Deep Dive</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]">BTC retested $65,000 · HL confirmed · Paper +$6,500</div>
        </div>
        <span class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]">→</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card p-6 bg-white/[0.02] border border-[var(--border)]">
    <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-3">Monthly Deep Dive Methodology</h3>
    <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-[var(--text-muted)]">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-primary mt-0.5">▸</span>Based on Al Brooks price action — focus on monthly/weekly structure</li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-primary mt-0.5">▸</span>Integrates on-chain data (exchange netflow, LTH balance change)</li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-primary mt-0.5">▸</span>Full monthly paper trading record, transparent P&L</li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-primary mt-0.5">▸</span>Next month plan: key levels + trigger conditions + risk management</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>

</BaseLayout>
